dataLineage.statement:
Layer was sent to ITOS as a zipped shapefile in an email from the IMO. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Admin3 name "O'yida" was given a reference name. 2. Admin3 names "Abela abaya" and "Gununo hamus town" were made Proper Case. 3. Fixed double space errors in Admin3 names "Kibet town", "Raya Alamata" and "Hobicha Abaya". 4. Admin3 units "Samurobi", "Adar", "Abaala" and "Abaala town" had their RefNames moved to their AltNames field. 5. Fixed 7 gap errors and 3 overlap errors.
The following was found by ITOS but not addressed in this version: 1. Admin3 "Odo Shakiso" and "Adama Tulu Jido Kombolcha" have potential multipart polygon errors. 2. The slashes and parentheses in some names suggest the presence of alternate names that should be separated and placed in an AltName field
